### ===========================================
### Book API — HTTP Tests (IntelliJ HTTP Client)
### Grünen Play-Button links klicken zum Ausführen
### ===========================================

### Alle Bücher abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books
Accept: application/json

### Ein Buch nach ID abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books/1
Accept: application/json

### Buch nicht gefunden (404)
GET http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books/999
Accept: application/json

### Neues Buch erstellen
POST http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Pragmatic Programmer",
  "author": "David Thomas",
  "isbn": "978-0135957059",
  "price": 49.99
}

### Noch ein Buch erstellen
POST http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Design Patterns",
  "author": "Gang of Four",
  "isbn": "978-0201633610",
  "price": 44.99
}

### Buch aktualisieren (ID 1)
PUT http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code (2nd Edition)",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "isbn": "978-0132350884",
  "price": 39.99
}

### Buch aktualisieren — nicht gefunden (404)
PUT http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ghost Book",
  "author": "Nobody",
  "isbn": "000-0000000000",
  "price": 0.01
}

### Buch löschen (ID 2)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books/2

### Buch nochmal löschen — nicht gefunden (404)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books/2

### Prüfen ob gelöscht — sollte 404 sein
GET http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books/2
Accept: application/json

### Alle Bücher nach dem Test
GET http://localhost:8080/ex01-rest-crud/api/books
Accept: application/json
